attributes.review: Never has an app been so obnoxious to keep someone who never should have had power in the first place in that position. Trump has never been or never will be a politician. He is just a businessman who had the funding to make people believe he had some right to be in office. And the app also gives us false information by not telling us before using the app that by supporting Donald Trump we are supporting white supremacy, racism, bigotry, homophobia, and misogyny. Terrible app, made by terrible people.
